```plantuml
@startuml castle-finance_vault-transaction-indexer

actor EventBridge as EB
participant "index-transaction-ids Lambda" as L1
participant SNS
participant SQS
participant "download-raw-transaction Lambda" as L2
participant DynamoDB_Raw as DB1
participant "normalize-raw-transaction Lambda" as L3
participant DynamoDB_Normalized as DB2
participant Solscan

EB -> L1: Trigger index-transaction-ids
L1 -> Solscan: Fetch transaction IDs
Solscan -> L1: Return transaction IDs
L1 -> SNS: Publish transaction IDs

SNS ->> SQS: Send message with transaction IDs
SQS ->> L2: Consume message

L2 -> Solscan: Fetch raw transaction data
Solscan -> L2: Return raw transaction data
L2 -> DB1: Store raw transaction data

DB1 -> L3: Trigger on data insert
L3 -> DB1: Fetch raw data
L3 -> L3: Normalize transaction data
L3 -> DB2: Store normalized transaction data

@enduml
```